Tuesday, September 11, 2001

MISCELLANEOUS DOCKET

In re Extension of Filing Deadline.

It appearing to the court that access to the Supreme Court Clerk’s Office was inhibited on September, 11, 2001,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that documents due to he filed in the Supreme Court by the deadline of September 11, 2001, may be accepted for filing on September 12, 2001.
